# sqlite-or-distribute

## Description

Migrated from the hand-coded `sqlite_inspired_rules` to a declarative `.rra` rule
(RFC 0090). The rewrite is expressed as structured data below.

## Rewrite

lhs: (or (and ?a ?b) (and ?a ?c))
rhs: (and ?a (or ?b ?c))
